### 修正対象 [context-monitor.sh](/Users/masayuki/.claude/hooks/context-monitor.sh) ### 修正内容（diff形式） ```diff diff --git a/hooks/context-monitor.sh b/hooks/context-monitor.sh index a039ee62..1dadd39a 100755 --- a/hooks/context-monitor.sh +++ b/hooks/context-monitor.sh @@ -12,6 +12,8 @@ umask 077 TRACE_FILE="$HOME/.claude/state/agent-trace.jsonl" CHECKPOINT_FILE="$HOME/.claude/state/.trace-checkpoint" SUGGEST_FLAG="$HOME/.claude/state/.handover-suggest-flag" +PRESSURE_LOG="$HOME/.claude/state/context-pressure.jsonl" +PRESSURE_STATE="$HOME/.claude/state/context-pressure.json" THRESHOLD=30 # tool calls between checkpoints (~85% context); Bash included since 2026-02-19 (was 40 before Bash) # Skip if trace file doesn't exist @@ -45,8 +47,11 @@ if [ "$current" -lt "$checkpoint" ]; then fi delta=$((current - checkpoint)) +timestamp=$(date -u +%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ) if [ "$delta" -ge "$THRESHOLD" ]; then + printf '{"timestamp":"%s","tool_calls_since_checkpoint":%s,"action":"handover_suggested","severity":"warning"}
' "$timestamp" "$delta" >> "$PRESSURE_LOG" + printf '{"pressure":"high","tool_calls":%s,"timestamp":"%s"}
' "$delta" "$timestamp" > "$PRESSURE_STATE" # Only suggest once per checkpoint cycle if [ -f "$SUGGEST_FLAG" ]; then read -r flag_val < "$SUGGEST_FLAG" 2>/dev/null @@ -66,4 +71,6 @@ if [ "$delta" -ge "$THRESHOLD" ]; then echo " /handover を実行してください（MANDATORY）" echo " 完了後に /compact で作業継続。" echo "" +else + printf '{"pressure":"normal","tool_calls":%s,"timestamp":"%s"}
' "$delta" "$timestamp" > "$PRESSURE_STATE" fi ``` ### 検証結果 `bash -n /Users/masayuki/.claude/hooks/context-monitor.sh` は成功しました。 仮定: `~/.claude/state/` は既存運用どおり存在する前提で、ディレクトリ作成処理は追加していません。既存スクリプトも同前提で動作しているため、変更範囲はそのまま維持しています。
